snippet.title: TEE OFF * Gameplay [DREAMCAST]
snippet.description:
Tee Off, known in Japan as Golf Shiyō Yo (ゴルフしようよ, Gorufu Shiyō Yo), is a video game developed and published by Bottom Up and Acclaim Entertainment in 1999-2000. 

NO EMULATOR USED!! 
Played on ORIGINAL CONSOLE & Upscaled with Framemeister/OSSC if old Gen Console.

Platform(s) 
Dreamcast

Release 
JP: December 9, 1999
INT: January 12, 2000

Genre(s) Sports

Mode(s) Single-player, multiplayer
